def transform(sequence):
    sequence_list = list(sequence)
    zeros = [digit for digit in sequence_list if digit == '0']
    others = [digit for digit in sequence_list if digit != '0']
    transformed_sequence = ''.join(zeros + others)
    return transformed_sequence
